&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Psychiatrist, Part-Time (Contract) role with Headspace:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Headspace is your lifelong guide to better mental health. We make mental health support accessible to everyone, no matter their background or experience. Through our flagship Headspace app, we provide mindfulness tools for everyday life, including meditations, sleepcasts, mindful movement and focus exercises. Our&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.headspace.com/enterprise&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt; enterprise offerings&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; combine this experience with a human-centered model of care, with coaching, therapy, psychiatry and EAP services under one roof. Our team of experts ranges from mental health clinicians, to Emmy award-winning producers and data scientists, working together as one to help millions of people around the world be healthier and more productive.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
